 how to implement this freedom by canonical\ntransformation of the intrinsic Hamiltonian. We also reinterpret and rectify\nsignificant work by B. Dittrich on the construction of `Dirac observables'.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2015 04:14:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Nov 2015 11:56:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2015 16:05:31 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 20 Mar 2016 18:08:54 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 17 Jan 2018 18:18:22 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Sun, 20 Jun 2021 23:20:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-22"}
